Story: Page Creation

  As an anonymous user
  I want to create new pages
  So that I can store information
  
  Scenario: Creating new page
  
    Given no pages in the system
    And an anonymous user
    
    When visiting '/' 
    And clicks on 'Neue Seite'
    
    Then user should see pages/new
    When fills in 'Title' with 'Some Title'
    And fills in 'Body' with 'some content'
    And clicks button 'Erstellen'
    
    Then the page should be saved
    